channel.title: Pro Coder Needs Work!
channel.description:
Greetings,
I am a professional Java coder. I am currently following a professional Java class , i already did easy and medium. I have a 6year Java experience behind me.
And currently i got to much free time, so i want to help someone out. I want to help you code on ur Runescape Private Server.
What do you need? A VPS ( recommended, or show me that your servers' uptime is 90%+ ) At least 15players online all the time.
It is totally free. I just want a nice community to work in.
For more information you can contact me on laurenz007@hotmail.com
Greetings
